bill.summary: 5/6/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend, through December 31, 1996, the duty on O,O-Dimethyl-S-(4-oxo-1,2,3-benzotriazin-3-(4H)-yl) methyl) phosphorodithioate.
